The data story I found for this week was from AP News, here is a link: https://apnews.com/article/russia-ukraine-war-ukraine-vladimir-putin-0000019c8ad8dd59afffcadd1e100000
It is an interactive story and map detailing the Russia-Ukraine War that includes pictures and data points on the map of all the Russian seized territory, battles, drone strikes, and other events. Although it is not tied to an event happening this week, I think it is a cool data visualization that makes the story more powerful. 
